Rogue OWE
---------
Decrypt trafik Wi-Fi OWE (Opportunistic Wireless Encryption) menggunakan kunci TK. 

Cara Instal
-----------
https://github.com/fixploit03/rogue-owe/blob/main/INSTAL

Cara Menggunakan
----------------
1. Jalankan Rogue AP
2. Capture trafik
3. Copy nilai kunci TK
4. Stop capture
5. Decrypt

Referensi
---------
- https://www.wi-fi.org/beacon/dan-harkins/wi-fi-certified-enhanced-open-transparent-wi-fi-protections-without-complexity
- https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc8110.html
- https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pertukaran_kunci_Diffie%E2%80%93Hellman
